00:25:09.605 --> 00:25:16.730 align:middle line:90%


00:25:16.730 --> 00:25:19.690 align:middle line:84%
And it started to take off
pretty well straight away it,

00:25:19.690 --> 00:25:22.780 align:middle line:84%
had all bluey, purple
lights around the bottom.

00:25:22.780 --> 00:25:24.610 align:middle line:84%
I don't remember
seeing any windows.

00:25:24.610 --> 00:25:27.370 align:middle line:84%
And it took off to about
probably 4 or 5 meters

00:25:27.370 --> 00:25:29.380 align:middle line:84%
in the air, and then
turned on its side,

00:25:29.380 --> 00:25:32.170 align:middle line:84%
and just went zoom,
straight up so

00:25:32.170 --> 00:25:35.710 align:middle line:84%
fast that there's
just nothing even now

00:25:35.710 --> 00:25:39.250 align:middle line:90%
day that could go that fast.

00:25:39.250 --> 00:25:41.560 align:middle line:84%
>> Shortly after
the object departed,

00:25:41.560 --> 00:25:44.830 align:middle line:84%
the authorities
converged on the school.

00:25:44.830 --> 00:25:49.750 align:middle line:10%
>> We had army, air force,
police down there cordoning off

00:25:49.750 --> 00:25:53.780 align:middle line:10%
the area to prevent any of us
entering the area or disturbing

00:25:53.780 --> 00:25:54.580 align:middle line:10%
anything.

00:25:54.580 --> 00:25:55.960 align:middle line:10%
>> We got called to assembly.

00:25:55.960 --> 00:25:59.230 align:middle line:10%
The headmaster said,
you have not seen this.

00:25:59.230 --> 00:26:00.610 align:middle line:90%
You do not talk about it.

00:26:00.610 --> 00:26:03.520 align:middle line:90%
You'll be in trouble if you do.

00:26:03.520 --> 00:26:07.750 align:middle line:10%
>> For the first time ever, the
school science teacher agreed

00:26:07.750 --> 00:26:10.600 align:middle line:10%
to describe what
he saw that day,

00:26:10.600 --> 00:26:13.240 align:middle line:10%
providing we concealed
his identity.

00:26:13.240 --> 00:26:14.680 align:middle line:10%
>> It was not a mirage.

00:26:14.680 --> 00:26:17.530 align:middle line:10%
There was something
physical in the sky.

00:26:17.530 --> 00:26:19.210 align:middle line:10%
It was silver.

00:26:19.210 --> 00:26:20.590 align:middle line:10%
It could hover.

00:26:20.590 --> 00:26:22.240 align:middle line:10%
It could move slowly.

00:26:22.240 --> 00:26:24.250 align:middle line:90%
It could move very rapidly.

00:26:24.250 --> 00:26:28.030 align:middle line:84%
Eventually, it moved away to
the other side of the oval

00:26:28.030 --> 00:26:30.400 align:middle line:90%
and down behind some pine trees.

00:26:30.400 --> 00:26:33.580 align:middle line:84%
I was not then
nor ever have been

00:26:33.580 --> 00:26:36.790 align:middle line:84%
able to use my
knowledge of the world

00:26:36.790 --> 00:26:42.020 align:middle line:84%
nor my scientific training to
provide a rational explanation.

00:26:42.020 --> 00:26:46.310 align:middle line:10%
>> What he said next sheds light
on why the school's staff have

00:26:46.310 --> 00:26:49.040 align:middle line:10%
remained silent all these years.

00:26:49.040 --> 00:26:50.870 align:middle line:84%
>> There was a knock
on the door one night.

00:26:50.870 --> 00:26:55.310 align:middle line:84%
Two older men, one in uniform,
asked for my description

00:26:55.310 --> 00:26:56.570 align:middle line:90%
of what I'd seen.

00:26:56.570 --> 00:26:59.480 align:middle line:84%
I was then told that I
hadn't seen anything,

00:26:59.480 --> 00:27:03.500 align:middle line:84%
but I'd made it all up,
possibly because I was drunk.

00:27:03.500 --> 00:27:05.810 align:middle line:84%
And that they would
have to report that fact

00:27:05.810 --> 00:27:07.160 align:middle line:90%
to the education department.

00:27:07.160 --> 00:27:09.060 align:middle line:90%
And I would lose my job.

00:27:09.060 --> 00:27:13.250 align:middle line:84%
After that, I was told
that I would be prosecuted

00:27:13.250 --> 00:27:14.810 align:middle line:90%
under the Official Secrets Act.

00:27:14.810 --> 00:27:18.530 align:middle line:84%
And I was told that there
wasn't anything there,

00:27:18.530 --> 00:27:22.100 align:middle line:84%
when I knew there was, and that
I had to keep quiet about it.

00:27:22.100 --> 00:27:26.010 align:middle line:90%


00:27:26.010 --> 00:27:27.390 align:middle line:90%
Why did I have to keep quiet?

00:27:27.390 --> 00:27:30.160 align:middle line:90%


00:27:30.160 --> 00:27:34.090 align:middle line:84%
>> The Westall landing may not
have been an isolated incident.

00:27:34.090 --> 00:27:38.890 align:middle line:84%
Four days prior, a then young
engineer in nearby Balwyn

00:27:38.890 --> 00:27:41.470 align:middle line:84%
was taking photos in
his mother's garden

00:27:41.470 --> 00:27:43.360 align:middle line:90%
when something caught his eye.

00:27:43.360 --> 00:27:44.830 align:middle line:84%
>> This tremendous
flash of light.

00:27:44.830 --> 00:27:48.100 align:middle line:84%
And I looked up and
I saw this object.

00:27:48.100 --> 00:27:49.300 align:middle line:90%
And I pulled--

00:27:49.300 --> 00:27:50.560 align:middle line:90%
I had a Polaroid camera.

00:27:50.560 --> 00:27:52.870 align:middle line:84%
I pulled this up, hit
myself on my face.

00:27:52.870 --> 00:27:55.420 align:middle line:90%
And I took the picture.

00:27:55.420 --> 00:27:56.690 align:middle line:90%
And I got the photograph here.

00:27:56.690 --> 00:27:58.455 align:middle line:84%
>> This is the
original Polaroid?

00:27:58.455 --> 00:27:59.255 align:middle line:90%
>> That's it.

00:27:59.255 --> 00:28:00.055 align:middle line:90%
It certainly is.

00:28:00.055 --> 00:28:08.870 align:middle line:90%


00:28:08.870 --> 00:28:11.270 align:middle line:84%
It looked like it was made
out of some form of metal

00:28:11.270 --> 00:28:12.680 align:middle line:90%
and it was engineered.

00:28:12.680 --> 00:28:18.157 align:middle line:84%
And being an engineer,
I was sure it was.

00:28:18.157 --> 00:28:19.740 align:middle line:84%
And that's when I
took the photograph,

00:28:19.740 --> 00:28:20.670 align:middle line:90%
and it tipped around.

00:28:20.670 --> 00:28:21.795 align:middle line:90%
And I could see the bottom.

00:28:21.795 --> 00:28:25.180 align:middle line:84%
And it looked like it
was rotating to me.

00:28:25.180 --> 00:28:26.430 align:middle line:90%
And that was it.

00:28:26.430 --> 00:28:29.100 align:middle line:84%
And then after that, it
sort of gave a bounce,

00:28:29.100 --> 00:28:32.910 align:middle line:84%
and it rocketed away to the
north at very high speed.

00:28:32.910 --> 00:28:35.530 align:middle line:84%
>> Can you describe
the acceleration?

00:28:35.530 --> 00:28:37.320 align:middle line:84%
>> It was like
almost instantaneous,

00:28:37.320 --> 00:28:39.330 align:middle line:84%
like it had been
shot out of a gun.

00:28:39.330 --> 00:28:42.270 align:middle line:90%
Wham, you know.

00:28:42.270 --> 00:28:45.210 align:middle line:84%
>> Air Force officers
showed up at his doorstep,

00:28:45.210 --> 00:28:48.510 align:middle line:84%
asking for every detail
of his experience.

00:28:48.510 --> 00:28:53.730 align:middle line:84%
>> And they also had some
photographs of similar things.

00:28:53.730 --> 00:28:56.520 align:middle line:84%
And they also had
a book, which had

00:28:56.520 --> 00:29:00.450 align:middle line:84%
pictures of things in which
they didn't leave with me.

00:29:00.450 --> 00:29:03.060 align:middle line:84%
The analysts had
to look through.

00:29:03.060 --> 00:29:08.850 align:middle line:84%
But they said it was an
unidentified flying object.

00:29:08.850 --> 00:29:10.680 align:middle line:90%
So that was it.

00:29:10.680 --> 00:29:13.050 align:middle line:90%
>> What was the implication?

00:29:13.050 --> 00:29:15.990 align:middle line:84%
>> That it didn't come
from anywhere on Earth.

00:29:15.990 --> 00:29:19.430 align:middle line:90%


00:29:19.430 --> 00:29:23.030 align:middle line:84%
>> Project Blue Book with
a skeletal staff continued

00:29:23.030 --> 00:29:26.390 align:middle line:84%
publicly collecting
thousands of cases.

00:29:26.390 --> 00:29:29.150 align:middle line:10%
Despite efforts to
explain them away,

00:29:29.150 --> 00:29:33.320 align:middle line:10%
hundreds were still
filed as unknown.

00:29:33.320 --> 00:29:37.355 align:middle line:10%
>> Several reports of a strange
egg-shaped object about 200

00:29:37.355 --> 00:29:40.940 align:middle line:10%
feet long landing on farms
and highways last night

00:29:40.940 --> 00:29:43.850 align:middle line:10%
in the vicinity of Levelland.

00:29:43.850 --> 00:29:46.340 align:middle line:10%
Sheriff Clem says
he even himself

00:29:46.340 --> 00:29:49.280 align:middle line:10%
