which somehow turned off

00:29:49.280 --> 00:29:52.070 align:middle line:10%
lights and auto engines
when it came near.

00:29:52.070 --> 00:29:56.630 align:middle line:10%
>> The object did take
off almost straight up

00:29:56.630 --> 00:30:00.050 align:middle line:10%
at a terrific speed.

00:30:00.050 --> 00:30:04.100 align:middle line:10%
>> Within 24 to 36 hours after
these sightings in Levelland,

00:30:04.100 --> 00:30:06.680 align:middle line:10%
Texas, at the White
Sands Proving Ground,

00:30:06.680 --> 00:30:09.590 align:middle line:10%
very close to the Trinity test
site where they first detonated

00:30:09.590 --> 00:30:14.690 align:middle line:10%
