personnel witnessed a glowing

00:30:14.690 --> 00:30:18.180 align:middle line:10%
egg-shaped object that
apparently landed.

00:30:18.180 --> 00:30:22.250 align:middle line:10%
>> This is Bill Haggard,
public information officer,

00:30:22.250 --> 00:30:26.090 align:middle line:10%
White Sands Proving
Ground, New Mexico.

00:30:26.090 --> 00:30:29.750 align:middle line:10%
What they saw looked like
a landing and takeoff

00:30:29.750 --> 00:30:32.450 align:middle line:10%
of some controlled
object from outer space.

00:30:32.450 --> 00:30:51.630 align:middle line:90%


00:30:51.630 --> 00:30:54.570 align:middle line:10%
>> Well, I was chasing
a car up Park Street.

00:30:54.570 --> 00:30:58.200 align:middle line:90%
It was reckless driving.

00:30:58.200 --> 00:31:01.360 align:middle line:10%
I saw this big
cloud of smoke, so I

00:31:01.360 --> 00:31:05.050 align:middle line:10%
decided to let go of the car
and go up there and investigate.

00:31:05.050 --> 00:31:08.740 align:middle line:10%
By the time I got there, I
could see a big white object

00:31:08.740 --> 00:31:10.890 align:middle line:10%
sitting in the arroyo.

00:31:10.890 --> 00:31:12.435 align:middle line:10%
I couldn't tell what
it was at first.

00:31:12.435 --> 00:31:18.800 align:middle line:90%


00:31:18.800 --> 00:31:20.040 align:middle line:10%
My radio was dead.

00:31:20.040 --> 00:31:21.305 align:middle line:10%
It didn't work at all.

00:31:21.305 --> 00:31:26.120 align:middle line:90%


00:31:26.120 --> 00:31:30.530 align:middle line:10%
I could see some figures,
looked like they were

00:31:30.530 --> 00:31:33.920 align:middle line:10%
walking around the craft there.

00:31:33.920 --> 00:31:37.940 align:middle line:84%
>> They appeared to be dressed
in white coveralls and were

00:31:37.940 --> 00:31:40.760 align:middle line:90%
child-like, that is small.

00:31:40.760 --> 00:31:44.690 align:middle line:10%
>> One was in front,
the other in back.

00:31:44.690 --> 00:31:48.290 align:middle line:84%
>> Zamora added that one of
the two persons turned his head

00:31:48.290 --> 00:31:50.120 align:middle line:90%
and looked straight at him.

00:31:50.120 --> 00:31:55.060 align:middle line:90%


00:31:55.060 --> 00:32:01.610 align:middle line:84%
>> When I got out of the
car, about 50 feet from it,

00:32:01.610 --> 00:32:05.060 align:middle line:84%
I guess they saw me because they
started their motor or whatever

00:32:05.060 --> 00:32:06.080 align:middle line:90%
it is.

00:32:06.080 --> 00:32:09.110 align:middle line:84%
I could see a big blast of fire
coming from right under it.

00:32:09.110 --> 00:32:12.010 align:middle line:90%


00:32:12.010 --> 00:32:15.280 align:middle line:84%
So I was behind some bushes
there, behind my car.

00:32:15.280 --> 00:32:19.600 align:middle line:84%
I could see it and I
could feel that heat.

00:32:19.600 --> 00:32:22.357 align:middle line:90%
That really got me scared.

00:32:22.357 --> 00:32:24.940 align:middle line:84%
A lot of people say, why don't
you take your gun out and shoot

00:32:24.940 --> 00:32:25.740 align:middle line:90%
at it?

00:32:25.740 --> 00:32:27.560 align:middle line:84%
And that they weren't
doing nothing to me.

00:32:27.560 --> 00:32:30.420 align:middle line:90%


00:32:30.420 --> 00:32:33.330 align:middle line:84%
It just took a little
while to get airborne,

00:32:33.330 --> 00:32:35.370 align:middle line:84%
came up a little bit
about 20, 30 feet,

00:32:35.370 --> 00:32:44.400 align:middle line:84%
and it stayed there a while,
in a state just as quiet

00:32:44.400 --> 00:32:45.200 align:middle line:90%
as it could be.

00:32:45.200 --> 00:32:48.240 align:middle line:90%


00:32:48.240 --> 00:32:50.590 align:middle line:90%
And then just flew away.

00:32:50.590 --> 00:32:51.390 align:middle line:90%
That's it.

00:32:51.390 --> 00:32:59.570 align:middle line:90%


00:32:59.570 --> 00:33:01.390 align:middle line:90%
>> Lonnie was very, very scared.

00:33:01.390 --> 00:33:02.860 align:middle line:90%
He was as white as a sheet.

00:33:02.860 --> 00:33:07.300 align:middle line:84%
From here, went directly to the
church to talk to the priest.

00:33:07.300 --> 00:33:10.750 align:middle line:10%
>> Pablo Lopez was among the
first to arrive at the landing

00:33:10.750 --> 00:33:12.160 align:middle line:10%
and takeoff site.

00:33:12.160 --> 00:33:14.620 align:middle line:84%
>> The ground was still
smoldering in some of the weeds

00:33:14.620 --> 00:33:15.760 align:middle line:90%
that were around it.

00:33:15.760 --> 00:33:19.720 align:middle line:84%
>> This rare footage gives us
a glimpse of the scene shortly

00:33:19.720 --> 00:33:21.490 align:middle line:90%
after the incident.

00:33:21.490 --> 00:33:25.300 align:middle line:84%
