That was about the
approximate size of them.

00:33:41.330 --> 00:33:44.990 align:middle line:84%
In comparison to a quarter,
that's pretty small.

00:33:44.990 --> 00:33:46.240 align:middle line:90%
That's about the size of them.

00:33:46.240 --> 00:33:48.760 align:middle line:90%


00:33:48.760 --> 00:33:51.920 align:middle line:10%
>> Within an hour and over
the next several days,

00:33:51.920 --> 00:33:54.340 align:middle line:10%
officials from
the FBI, military,

00:33:54.340 --> 00:33:58.165 align:middle line:10%
