00:34:18.159 --> 00:34:18.959 align:middle line:90%
side.

00:34:18.959 --> 00:34:25.050 align:middle line:90%


00:34:25.050 --> 00:34:27.134 align:middle line:84%
>> Of course, the
burn area there.

00:34:27.134 --> 00:34:28.700 align:middle line:90%
>> I was behind my car.

00:34:28.700 --> 00:34:30.450 align:middle line:84%
I could see it and I
could feel that heat.

00:34:30.450 --> 00:34:33.600 align:middle line:90%


00:34:33.600 --> 00:34:35.310 align:middle line:84%
They told me that
all over the state,

00:34:35.310 --> 00:34:38.100 align:middle line:84%
they had been seen some
of those flying saucers

00:34:38.100 --> 00:34:39.600 align:middle line:90%
or whatever you call them.

00:34:39.600 --> 00:34:42.070 align:middle line:90%
They gave me a book on it.

00:34:42.070 --> 00:34:44.159 align:middle line:84%
And they told me to
go ahead and read it.

00:34:44.159 --> 00:34:48.120 align:middle line:84%
And well, it says not
to say nothing on it.

00:34:48.120 --> 00:34:49.020 align:middle line:90%
Keep away from it.

00:34:49.020 --> 00:34:51.210 align:middle line:90%
Don't say too much.

00:34:51.210 --> 00:34:54.030 align:middle line:84%
>> It was the middle of the
