00:34:54.030 --> 00:34:55.739 align:middle line:90%
home.

00:34:55.739 --> 00:34:59.070 align:middle line:90%
>> Well, he was real pale.

00:34:59.070 --> 00:35:00.180 align:middle line:90%
And I thought he was sick.

00:35:00.180 --> 00:35:01.780 align:middle line:10%
I said, are you
sick or something?

00:35:01.780 --> 00:35:02.580 align:middle line:10%
He said, no.

00:35:02.580 --> 00:35:03.840 align:middle line:10%
He said, I was just working.

00:35:03.840 --> 00:35:07.065 align:middle line:84%
He was like--
like, he was angry.

00:35:07.065 --> 00:35:09.620 align:middle line:90%


