He said it's just a headache.

00:35:22.816 --> 00:35:24.840 align:middle line:10%
He said everybody's after me.

00:35:24.840 --> 00:35:29.410 align:middle line:84%
And some believe
me and some don't.

00:35:29.410 --> 00:35:31.030 align:middle line:90%
>> Dear Mr. Zamora.

00:35:31.030 --> 00:35:31.920 align:middle line:90%
>> Dear Mr. Zamora.

00:35:31.920 --> 00:35:35.750 align:middle line:84%
>> Dear Mr. Zamora,
