00:36:52.050 --> 00:36:54.810 align:middle line:90%
of the President.

00:36:54.810 --> 00:37:02.080 align:middle line:84%
To this day, the Socorro close
encounter remains unexplained.

00:37:02.080 --> 00:37:06.670 align:middle line:10%
>> Socorro was very similar
