jets were shot by shortly

00:42:33.270 --> 00:42:35.600 align:middle line:90%
after I filmed the disks.

00:42:35.600 --> 00:42:39.830 align:middle line:84%
I could not see any exhaust,
wings, or any kind of fuselage.

00:42:39.830 --> 00:42:42.140 align:middle line:84%
They appear to be of
a bright shiny metal,

00:42:42.140 --> 00:42:43.400 align:middle line:90%
like polished silver.

00:42:43.400 --> 00:42:47.000 align:middle line:90%


00:42:47.000 --> 00:42:51.440 align:middle line:10%
>> There are cases that are
not explainable in conventional

00:42:51.440 --> 00:42:52.460 align:middle line:10%
terms.

00:42:52.460 --> 00:42:55.070 align:middle line:10%
There is the assumption
of intelligence

00:42:55.070 --> 00:42:59.990 align:middle line:10%
or intelligent control but
not necessarily the assumption

00:42:59.990 --> 00:43:01.670 align:middle line:10%
of direct communication.

00:43:01.670 --> 00:43:03.810 align:middle line:90%
Why are they here?

00:43:03.810 --> 00:43:05.180 align:middle line:90%
What are they doing?

00:43:05.180 --> 00:43:06.740 align:middle line:90%
What do they want from us?

00:43:06.740 --> 00:43:09.700 align:middle line:90%
What are their motivations?

00:43:09.700 --> 00:43:13.570 align:middle line:84%
>> But it was Dr. Condon
who wrote the final word.

00:43:13.570 --> 00:43:17.620 align:middle line:10%
"There appears to be no
verified and fully satisfactory

00:43:17.620 --> 00:43:20.770 align:middle line:10%
evidence of any
case that is clearly

00:43:20.770 --> 00:43:24.250 align:middle line:10%
outside the framework of
presently known science

00:43:24.250 --> 00:43:26.350 align:middle line:10%
and technology."

00:43:26.350 --> 00:43:29.650 align:middle line:10%
>> Oh, I wouldn't count
really on that one.

00:43:29.650 --> 00:43:33.760 align:middle line:10%
You'd have to conclude that's
what we were looking at

00:43:33.760 --> 00:43:37.300 align:middle line:10%
was beyond our current
state of the knowledge.

00:43:37.300 --> 00:43:39.220 align:middle line:10%
>> But it began
to hit me that Dr.

00:43:39.220 --> 00:43:42.170 align:middle line:10%
Condon has apparently not
read his own material very

00:43:42.170 --> 00:43:42.970 align:middle line:10%
carefully.

00:43:42.970 --> 00:43:44.680 align:middle line:10%
When you do an actual
tabulation, which

00:43:44.680 --> 00:43:45.970 align:middle line:10%
he doesn't seem to
have done, and you

00:43:45.970 --> 00:43:47.410 align:middle line:10%
find his percentage
of unexplained

00:43:47.410 --> 00:43:49.660 align:middle line:10%
is five to six times
larger than the Air Force.

00:43:49.660 --> 00:43:51.940 align:middle line:84%
And yet what is his
principal recommendation?

00:43:51.940 --> 00:43:53.800 align:middle line:84%
The principal recommendation
that Dr. Condon

00:43:53.800 --> 00:43:56.425 align:middle line:84%
has come through with is there's
nothing of scientific interest

00:43:56.425 --> 00:43:58.360 align:middle line:84%
that warrants further
attention on the part

00:43:58.360 --> 00:44:00.370 align:middle line:84%
of the federal government
here in any major way.

00:44:00.370 --> 00:44:03.370 align:middle line:84%
He recommends dropping
the whole problem.

00:44:03.370 --> 00:44:07.180 align:middle line:84%
>> Nobody could get funded,
nobody would look at the data

00:44:07.180 --> 00:44:12.910 align:middle line:84%
seriously because of the
prestige of the academy saying

00:44:12.910 --> 00:44:14.620 align:middle line:84%
that the problem
had been solved.

00:44:14.620 --> 00:44:18.500 align:middle line:84%
The Air Force closed
their reporting system.

00:44:18.500 --> 00:44:21.850 align:middle line:84%
So that if the public
wanted to report something,

00:44:21.850 --> 00:44:24.290 align:middle line:84%
they would report it
to the local police,

00:44:24.290 --> 00:44:28.600 align:middle line:84%
but it would never get to the
attention of scientists really

00:44:28.600 --> 00:44:32.390 align:middle line:90%
examining the phenomenon.

00:44:32.390 --> 00:44:37.370 align:middle line:84%
>> In 1969, the Air Force
officially ended its public

00:44:37.370 --> 00:44:38.290 align:middle line:90%
investigations.

00:44:38.290 --> 00:44:41.120 align:middle line:90%


00:44:41.120 --> 00:44:43.720 align:middle line:10%
>> Which would suggest what?

00:44:43.720 --> 00:44:47.330 align:middle line:10%
That they knew what it was?

00:44:47.330 --> 00:44:49.940 align:middle line:10%
>> Or didn't know what it was.

00:44:49.940 --> 00:44:53.906 align:middle line:84%
