00:48:11.790 --> 00:48:14.066 align:middle line:90%
Essentially, they were disabled.

00:48:14.066 --> 00:48:15.880 align:middle line:90%
>> Channel 11.

00:48:15.880 --> 00:48:20.230 align:middle line:84%
